oji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心唔明。話晒專業人士入息唔差，啲女一係好積極一係完全唔理你。我睇唔透</blockquote><br />\n好葡萄高中已經開始一齊幾十年再結婚果啲情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人大左真心難求</blockquote><br />\nYes. 宜家太積極果啲我都有戒心</blockquote><br />\n但唔積極又唔會成事，又怕錯過左，真係好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4497084d20ac781d76be0716d905716c99df921","tid":316220,"uid":17958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"成日比人話好仔 都冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac4176ee796c60e6c5ecf3f70fb31565e511ed3","tid":316220,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"你有freestyle嗎？"},{"pid":"4125803d87bfe2395787241a20c48477e96b178d","tid":316220,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日比人話好仔 都冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98643ca4245ee1612172c54f82601a282baba471","tid":316220,"uid":17958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日比人話好仔 都冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係同我講 收風收返黎"},{"pid":"635f8c8cd4a56e666de098e21dd2357ef90c695b","tid":316220,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dc592d4c2f007b403d5d6b6067d78b3dc85813f","tid":316220,"uid":2655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep